title: question on running the demo code
body:
Hi , after installing different dependencies on ubuntu 16.04 , for your project . I come across this error . I am wondering if there is something i am missing in this regards ?? ? 
snippet below . I am however using virtual machine for ubuntu 

```
python webcam_demo.py
```
